OL,3,CCould the Riverside Festival make a
OL,4,Creturn to Nottingham?
OL,6,FNottingham's popular Riverside
OL,7,FFestival could return next year after
OL,8,Fbeing scaled back in 2024.
OL,10,FThe free family event, held each
OL,11,Fsummer at the Victoria Embankment,
OL,12,Fhasn't taken place for the past two
OL,13,Fyears after being hit by the council's
OL,14,Ffinancial problems.
OL,16,FBut now there's fresh hope it could
OL,17,Freturn next year, with the City
OL,18,FCouncil saying its improving finances
OL,19,Fmean early planning can begin.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
