OL,3,CCould the Riverside Festival make a
OL,4,Creturn to Nottingham?
OL,6,FThe authority says it could go ahead
OL,7,Fin 2027.
OL,9,FCouncillor David Mellen is the
OL,10,Fexecutive member for Leisure Culture
OL,11,Fand Tourism chair at the authority.
OL,13,FHe said: "We were sad when Riverside
OL,14,Fhad to go. We had to make hard choices
OL,15,Fgiven the reduction in money that we
OL,16,Fgot from central government, the last
OL,17,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
